        "description": "Complete REST API collection for Material Management module in Odoo 14.\n\n**Setup Instructions:**\n1. Start Odoo with: `python3 odoo-bin -d your_database --addons-path=addons,custom_addons`\n2. Install 'Material Management' module via Apps menu\n3. Update collection variables if using different port\n\n**Proper REST API:**\n- GET requests use query parameters (no body)\n- POST/PUT/DELETE use JSON-RPC format in body\n- Clean and semantic HTTP methods\n\n**Authentication:** Public (no session required)\n**Base URL:** http://localhost:14100",
